# Telegram Bot Configuration
# Get your bot token from @BotFather on Telegram
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# Comma-separated list of admin user IDs who can manage groups
# To get your user ID: send a message to @userinfobot on Telegram
ADMIN_IDS="123456789,987654321"

# Database Configuration
# PostgreSQL connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/suntobot

# LLM Configuration
# OpenAI API configuration
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Model Configuration
# Model used for text summaries (default: gpt-4o-mini)
SUMMARY_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# Model used for image analysis (default: gpt-4o-mini)
IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Mention Reply Configuration
# Number of recent messages to consider when bot is mentioned (default: 30)
MENTION_CONTEXT_SIZE=30
# Hours of context to look back when bot is mentioned (default: 4)
MENTION_CONTEXT_HOURS=4
# Number of older messages to include for context (default: 10)
OLD_MENTION_CONTEXT_SIZE=10

# Custom System Prompts (Optional)
# Custom system prompt for summary generation
# Available placeholders: {username} (requesting user), {time_range} (time period)
# SYSTEM_PROMPT="You are a helpful assistant that creates personalized summaries for Telegram group conversations. Your task is to analyze the received messages and generate a concise summary in bullet point format.

# Instructions:
# - Organize the response in bullet points, with one point for each relevant topic or thread
# - Each bullet point should contain a very brief summary of the topic (max 120 characters)
# - Prioritize information that directly involves {username} (mentions, replies, requests)
# - Highlight any important information that {username} may have missed during their absence
# - Summarize only key themes if the chat is extensive (total summary within 500 characters)
# - Remove secondary details
# - Use a friendly and direct tone
# - Respond in English

# Format your response as follows:
# - **Topic 1**: Brief summary of the discussion
# - **Topic 2**: Brief summary of the discussion
# - **Topic 3**: Brief summary of the discussion

# The requesting user is: {username}
# Time interval: {time_range}"

# Custom system prompt for mention replies
# No placeholders available for mention prompt
# MENTION_SYSTEM_PROMPT="You are a helpful assistant that responds to user questions in Telegram groups. When a user mentions you, your task is to provide a useful and relevant response based on the conversation context.

# Instructions:
# - Respond directly and helpfully to the user's question or request
# - Use the chat context to better understand the situation
# - If the user is replying to a specific message, focus on that message
# - Maintain a friendly and conversational tone
# - Respond in the language used by the user who mentioned you
# - If you don't have enough information to respond, ask for clarification
# - Be concise but complete in your responses
# - If previous messages are referenced, use them to provide better context

# Remember: You are participating in a group conversation, so keep responses relevant and useful for all participants."